The vortex brightened. Out of it came the one known as allanon. His spark 
rekindeled At the place which he once called home. Now that the primals had 
pretty much one the war on cybertron he had to find a new place and a new 
groups to settle. Ultra Magnus had told stories of the ones called the 
alliance. They sounded sutible enough. He searched on his long scanners for 
any bots with that type of signature. He picked up a large group. It was a 
base maybe two. Hw would go there and see what he finds.
